            {
              "id": "CWE-219",
              "name": "StorageOfFileWithSensitiveDataUnderWebRoot",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product stores sensitive data under the web document root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Besides public-facing web pages and code, products may store sensitive data, code that is not directly invoked, or other files under the web document root of the web server. If the server is not configured or otherwise used to prevent direct access to those files, then attackers may obtain this sensitive data."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product stores sensitive data under the web document root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product stores sensitive data under the web document root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties.\n\n## Extended Description\n\nBesides public-facing web pages and code, products may store sensitive data, code that is not directly invoked, or other files under the web document root of the web server. If the server is not configured or otherwise used to prevent direct access to those files, then attackers may obtain this sensitive data.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Confidentiality. **Impact**: Read Application Data.\n\n## Potential Mitigations\n\n1. *Phase: Implementation, System Configuration*. Avoid storing information under the web root directory.\n2. *Phase: System Configuration*. Access control permissions should be set to prevent reading/writing of sensitive files inside/outside of the web directory."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/219.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Storage of File with Sensitive Data Under Web Root",
                "cwe/status": "Draft",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-552"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-220",
              "name": "StorageOfFileWithSensitiveDataUnderFtpRoot",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product stores sensitive data under the FTP server root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product stores sensitive data under the FTP server root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product stores sensitive data under the FTP server root with insufficient access control, which might make it accessible to untrusted parties.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Confidentiality. **Impact**: Read Application Data.\n\n## Potential Mitigations\n\n1. *Phase: Implementation, System Configuration*. Avoid storing information under the FTP root directory.\n2. *Phase: System Configuration*. Access control permissions should be set to prevent reading/writing of sensitive files inside/outside of the FTP directory."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/220.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Storage of File With Sensitive Data Under FTP Root",
                "cwe/status": "Draft",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-552"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-221",
              "name": "InformationLossOrOmission",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product does not record, or improperly records, security-relevant information that leads to an incorrect decision or hampers later analysis."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product does not record, or improperly records, security-relevant information that leads to an incorrect decision or hampers later analysis.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product does not record, or improperly records, security-relevant information that leads to an incorrect decision or hampers later analysis.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Non-Repudiation. **Impact**: Hide Activities."
              },
