            {
              "id": "CWE-222",
              "name": "TruncationOfSecurityRelevantInformation",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product truncates the display, recording, or processing of security-relevant information in a way that can obscure the source or nature of an attack."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product truncates the display, recording, or processing of security-relevant information in a way that can obscure the source or nature of an attack.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product truncates the display, recording, or processing of security-relevant information in a way that can obscure the source or nature of an attack.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Non-Repudiation. **Impact**: Hide Activities.\n  - The source of an attack will be difficult or impossible to determine. This can allow attacks to the system to continue without notice."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/222.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Truncation of Security-relevant Information",
                "cwe/status": "Draft",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Base",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-221"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-223",
              "name": "OmissionOfSecurityRelevantInformation",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product does not record or display information that would be important for identifying the source or nature of an attack, or determining if an action is safe."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product does not record or display information that would be important for identifying the source or nature of an attack, or determining if an action is safe.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product does not record or display information that would be important for identifying the source or nature of an attack, or determining if an action is safe.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Non-Repudiation. **Impact**: Hide Activities.\n  - The source of an attack will be difficult or impossible to determine. This can allow attacks to the system to continue without notice."
              },
