                "text": "The product does not handle or incorrectly handles an exceptional condition.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product does not handle or incorrectly handles an exceptional condition.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Other."
              },
