                "cwe/abstraction": "Class",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-138"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-791",
              "name": "IncompleteFilteringOfSpecialElements",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter special elements before sending it to a downstream component."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter special elements before sending it to a downstream component.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter special elements before sending it to a downstream component.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Integrity. **Impact**: Unexpected State."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/791.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Incomplete Filtering of Special Elements",
                "cwe/status": "Incomplete",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Base",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-790"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-792",
              "name": "IncompleteFilteringOfOneOrMoreInstancesOfSpecialElements",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter one or more instances of special elements before sending it to a downstream component."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Incomplete filtering of this nature involves either: only filtering a single instance of a special element when more exist, or not filtering all instances or all elements where multiple special elements exist."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter one or more instances of special elements before sending it to a downstream component.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product receives data from an upstream component, but does not completely filter one or more instances of special elements before sending it to a downstream component.\n\n## Extended Description\n\nIncomplete filtering of this nature involves either: only filtering a single instance of a special element when more exist, or not filtering all instances or all elements where multiple special elements exist.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Integrity. **Impact**: Unexpected State."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/792.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Incomplete Filtering of One or More Instances of Special Elements",
                "cwe/status": "Incomplete",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-791"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-793",
              "name": "OnlyFilteringOneInstanceOfASpecialElement",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but only filters a single instance of a special element before sending it to a downstream component."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Incomplete filtering of this nature may be location-dependent, as in only the first or last element is filtered."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but only filters a single instance of a special element before sending it to a downstream component.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product receives data from an upstream component, but only filters a single instance of a special element before sending it to a downstream component.\n\n## Extended Description\n\nIncomplete filtering of this nature may be location-dependent, as in only the first or last element is filtered.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Integrity. **Impact**: Unexpected State."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/793.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Only Filtering One Instance of a Special Element",
                "cwe/status": "Incomplete",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-792"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-794",
              "name": "IncompleteFilteringOfMultipleInstancesOfSpecialElements",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not filter all instances of a special element before sending it to a downstream component."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Incomplete filtering of this nature may be applied to: sequential elements (special elements that appear next to each other) or non-sequential elements (special elements that appear multiple times in different locations)."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but does not filter all instances of a special element before sending it to a downstream component.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product receives data from an upstream component, but does not filter all instances of a special element before sending it to a downstream component.\n\n## Extended Description\n\nIncomplete filtering of this nature may be applied to: sequential elements (special elements that appear next to each other) or non-sequential elements (special elements that appear multiple times in different locations).\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Integrity. **Impact**: Unexpected State."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/794.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Incomplete Filtering of Multiple Instances of Special Elements",
                "cwe/status": "Incomplete",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-792"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-795",
              "name": "OnlyFilteringSpecialElementsAtASpecifiedLocation",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but only accounts for special elements at a specified location, thereby missing remaining special elements that may exist before sending it to a downstream component."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A filter might only account for instances of special elements when they occur: relative to a marker (e.g. \"at the beginning/end of string; the second argument\"), or at an absolute position (e.g. \"byte number 10\"). This may leave special elements in the data that did not match the filter position, but still may be dangerous."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product receives data from an upstream component, but only accounts for special elements at a specified location, thereby missing remaining special elements that may exist before sending it to a downstream component.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product receives data from an upstream component, but only accounts for special elements at a specified location, thereby missing remaining special elements that may exist before sending it to a downstream component.\n\n## Extended Description\n\nA filter might only account for instances of special elements when they occur: relative to a marker (e.g. \"at the beginning/end of string; the second argument\"), or at an absolute position (e.g. \"byte number 10\"). This may leave special elements in the data that did not match the filter position, but still may be dangerous.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Integrity. **Impact**: Unexpected State."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/795.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Only Filtering Special Elements at a Specified Location",
