            {
              "id": "CWE-1058",
              "name": "InvokableControlElementInMultiThreadContextWithNonFinalStaticStorableOrMemberElement",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The code contains a function or method that operates in a multi-threaded environment but owns an unsafe non-final static storable or member data element."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The code contains a function or method that operates in a multi-threaded environment but owns an unsafe non-final static storable or member data element.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe code contains a function or method that operates in a multi-threaded environment but owns an unsafe non-final static storable or member data element.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Reduce Reliability.\n  - This issue can prevent the product from running reliably. If the relevant code is reachable by an attacker, then this reliability problem might introduce a vulnerability."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/1058.html",
