                "text": "The code has a parent class that contains references to a child class, its methods, or its members."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The code has a parent class that contains references to a child class, its methods, or its members.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe code has a parent class that contains references to a child class, its methods, or its members.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Reduce Reliability.\n  - This issue can prevent the product from running reliably. If the relevant code is reachable by an attacker, then this reliability problem might introduce a vulnerability."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/1062.html",
