              "id": "CWE-1065",
              "name": "RuntimeResourceManagementControlElementInAComponentBuiltToRunOnApplicationServers",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product uses deployed components from application servers, but it also uses low-level functions/methods for management of resources, instead of the API provided by the application server."
