                "cwe/parent": "CWE-710"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-1069",
              "name": "EmptyExceptionBlock",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "An invokable code block contains an exception handling block that does not contain any code, i.e. is empty."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "An invokable code block contains an exception handling block that does not contain any code, i.e. is empty.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nAn invokable code block contains an exception handling block that does not contain any code, i.e. is empty.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Reduce Reliability.\n  - When an exception handling block (such as a Catch and Finally block) is used, but that block is empty, this can prevent the product from running reliably. If the relevant code is reachable by an attacker, then this reliability problem might introduce a vulnerability.\n\n## Potential Mitigations\n\n1. *Phase: Implementation*. For every exception block add code that handles the specific exception in the way intended by the application."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/1069.html",
              "properties": {
                "cwe/title": "Empty Exception Block",
                "cwe/status": "Incomplete",
                "cwe/abstraction": "Variant",
                "cwe/parent": "CWE-1071"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CWE-1070",
              "name": "SerializableDataElementContainingNonSerializableItemElements",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The product contains a serializable, storable data element such as a field or member, but the data element contains member elements that are not serializable."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The product contains a serializable, storable data element such as a field or member, but the data element contains member elements that are not serializable.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe product contains a serializable, storable data element such as a field or member, but the data element contains member elements that are not serializable.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Reduce Reliability.\n  - This issue can prevent the product from running reliably. If the relevant code is reachable by an attacker, then this reliability problem might introduce a vulnerability."
              },
