            {
              "id": "CWE-1127",
              "name": "CompilationWithInsufficientWarningsOrErrors",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The code is compiled without sufficient warnings enabled, which may prevent the detection of subtle bugs or quality issues."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "The code is compiled without sufficient warnings enabled, which may prevent the detection of subtle bugs or quality issues.",
                "markdown": "## Description\n\nThe code is compiled without sufficient warnings enabled, which may prevent the detection of subtle bugs or quality issues.\n\n## Common Consequences\n\n- **Scope**: Other. **Impact**: Reduce Maintainability.\n  - This issue makes it more difficult to maintain the product, which indirectly affects security by making it more difficult or time-consuming to find and/or fix vulnerabilities. It also might make it easier to introduce vulnerabilities."
              },
